Package org.hibernate.mapping

Class Formula

java.lang.Object
org.hibernate.mapping.Formula
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Selectable
public final class Formula extends Object implements Selectable, Serializable
A mapping model object representing a SQL formula which is used as a "derived" Column in an entity mapping.
